  "time_ut": 1656564160,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u201c\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd\u201d \u0bb5\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"I will not be impatient anymore,\" the northern governor warned",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Northern Province Governor Jeevan Thiagaraja has warned that he will not take action against the ministries and departments that have not yet presented solutions regarding the complaints and requests presented by the public and the affected parties to the heads of Northern Province Ministries and Departments.",
        "The Public Service in the Northern Province should be duly carried out by the Ministries of Transfer of Ministers.",
        "I have received many complaints directly from the public regarding the dissatisfaction of the public in the Ministries and Departments and the malpractices in the Ministries.",
        "It has been brought to my attention in the series that so far the Ministries and Heads of Departments have not taken action on some of the complaints so received.",
        "It is the duty of the responsible authorities to present a solution in a timely manner to the person making the complaint in accordance with the Government Circulars.",
        "While public administration is seen as an institutional structure built to ease the needs of the common people, when the public's needs are fulfilled through it, the said institution will win the trust of the people.",
        "The governor is not going to allow any administrative structure in the Northern Province to cause inconvenience to the people without functioning.",
        "Therefore, the governor warned that he will not hesitate to take action against those who have not presented solutions regarding the complaints given to the ministries and departments in the Northern Province. (R)"
      ],
